title: I Was Summoned to Another World as a Savior, but Because I’m in My Thirties That’s Impossible, so I Quietly Started a Book Café. - Novel Updates
tags: Adapted to Manga   Bookworm   Calm Protagonist   Female Protagonist   Knights   Magic   Multiple Transported Individuals   Protagonist Strong from the Start   Transported to Another World
author: Izumi Kyouka   和泉杏花
description:
Tsukina was summoned by God to another world to be one of its Saviors.

'I’ll leave saving the world to the younger Saviors, and open a book café and live how I want to!'

But will her encounter with the knight Ill, who arrives as a customer, disturb her quiet lifestyle?!>
